flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[User runs CLI command]
    B --> C[Parse arguments]

    C --> D{Is test_path provided?}
    D -- No --> E[Show error message]
    E --> Z([End])

    D -- Yes --> F[Create TestRunner]
    F --> G[Run test by test_path]
    G --> H[Execute pytest using subprocess]
    H --> I[Collect exit_code, stdout, stderr]
    I --> J[Create ExecutionResult]

    J --> K{exit_code == 0?}
    K -- Yes --> L[Print PASSED summary]
    K -- No --> M[Print FAILED summary]

    L --> Z([End])
    M --> Z([End])
